Name: Concept 20
About the game: Concept 20 consist of the following gameplays. - Controlling only the ball you will jump your way into the yellow box. - With the help of a flat bar, you will pick up the ball and try to traverse through all obstacles. - With the help of numbered blocks you will must figure out a way to get to the yellow box. - With 10 bars you will designs a path through various obstacles to complete the level.
